{"tid":1213493,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"催淚彈應對方法","createTime":"2019-06-13T01:51:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T01:55:21.000Z","uid":222301,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8d249d885582962792a8a1b35b8a9c566552b69f","tid":1213493,"uid":222301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:51:02.000Z","msg":"由琴日掟催淚彈既時候撻Q個張gif睇到, 個彈應該係一個暖水壼咁上下大既樽.<br />\n應該可以將一個5L至10L左右既水筒, cut開個底就可以cup住個催淚彈.<br />\n然後係樽頂入水位淋水入去將個彈淋熄.<br />\n睇返其實上年有人好有組織咁見到一有彈就衝埋去淋熄佢.<br />\n希望呢個方法幫到大家, 都希望今年有人整到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b0cfa93937807212a898adb349dc88eed47283f","tid":1213493,"uid":222301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:55:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f9iekeJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff9iekeJ.jpg&h=b29b1e2a&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}